---

<section
    id="capacidades"
    class="py-24 px-6 lg:px-20 max-w-7xl mx-auto w-full bg-white dark:bg-gray-900"
>
    <div class="flex flex-col mb-12">
        <h2
            class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white font-sans"
        >
            Capacidades Técnicas
        </h2>
        <div class="h-1.5 w-20 bg-cyan-700 dark:bg-cyan-500 rounded-full"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <!-- Software Engineering Card -->
        <div
            class="group p-1 rounded-2xl bg-surface-soft dark:bg-gray-800 border border-border-subtle dark:border-border-subtle-dark hover:border-cyan-200 dark:hover:border-cyan-900 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300"
        >
            <div
                class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 h-full rounded-xl p-8 flex flex-col gap-6 relative overflow-hidden"
            >
                <!-- Background Icon Decor -->
                <div
                    class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-[0.03] dark:opacity-[0.05] group-hover:opacity-[0.08] transition-opacity"
                >
                    <span
                        class="material-symbols-outlined text-9xl text-gray-900 dark:text-white"
                    >
                        architecture
                    </span>
                </div>

                <!-- Float Icon -->
                <div
                    class="size-12 rounded-lg bg-cyan-50 dark:bg-cyan-900/30 flex items-center justify-center text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400 group-hover:bg-cyan-700 dark:group-hover:bg-cyan-500 group-hover:text-white transition-colors"
                >
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl"
                        >deployed_code</span
                    >
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h3
                        class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2 font-sans"
                    >
                        Ingeniería de Software
                    </h3>
                    <p
                        class="text-text-description dark:text-text-description-dark leading-relaxed font-normal font-body"
                    >
                        Arquitectura robusta para sistemas críticos. Desarrollo
                        backend de alto rendimiento y diseño de microservicios
                        escalables.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <ul
                    class="space-y-3 mt-auto border-t border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800 pt-6"
                >
                    <li
                        class="flex items-center gap-3 text-text-description dark:text-text-description-dark"
                    >
                        <span
                            class="material-symbols-outlined text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400 text-sm"
                        >
                            check_circle
                        </span>
                        API Design & Integration
                    </li>
                    <li
                        class="flex items-center gap-3 text-text-description dark:text-text-description-dark"
                    >
                        <span
                            class="material-symbols-outlined text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400 text-sm"
                        >
                            check_circle
                        </span>
                        High Scalability Infrastructure
                    </li>
                    <li
                        class="flex items-center gap-3 text-text-description dark:text-text-description-dark"
                    >
                        <span
                            class="material-symbols-outlined text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400 text-sm"
                        >
                            check_circle
                        </span>
                        Database Optimization (SQL/NoSQL)
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- AI Card -->
        <div
            class="group p-1 rounded-2xl bg-surface-soft dark:bg-gray-800 border border-border-subtle dark:border-border-subtle-dark hover:border-cyan-200 dark:hover:border-cyan-900 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300"
        >
            <div
                class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 h-full rounded-xl p-8 flex flex-col gap-6 relative overflow-hidden"
            >
                <!-- Background Icon Decor -->
                <div
                    class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-[0.03] dark:opacity-[0.05] group-hover:opacity-[0.08] transition-opacity"
                >
                    <span
                        class="material-symbols-outlined text-9xl text-gray-900 dark:text-white"
                    >
                        smart_toy
                    </span>
                </div>

                <!-- Float Icon -->
                <div
                    class="size-12 rounded-lg bg-cyan-50 dark:bg-cyan-900/30 flex items-center justify-center text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400 group-hover:bg-cyan-700 dark:group-hover:bg-cyan-500 group-hover:text-white transition-colors"
                >
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-3xl"
                        >auto_fix_high</span
                    >
                </div>

                <div>
                    <h3
                        class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2 font-sans"
                    >
                        Automatización e IA Aplicada
                    </h3>
                    <p
                        class="text-text-description dark:text-text-description-dark leading-relaxed font-normal font-body"
                    >
                        Optimización de flujos de trabajo con inteligencia
                        artificial. Integración de modelos de lenguaje en
                        procesos de negocio.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <ul
                    class="space-y-3 mt-auto border-t border-border-subtle dark:border-border-subtle-dark pt-6"
                >
                    <li
                        class="flex items-center gap-3 text-text-description dark:text-text-description-dark"
                    >
                        <span
                            class="material-symbols-outlined text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400 text-sm"
                        >
                            check_circle
                        </span>
                        LLM Integration (OpenAI, Anthropic)
                    </li>
                    <li
                        class="flex items-center gap-3 text-text-description dark:text-text-description-dark"
                    >
                        <span
                            class="material-symbols-outlined text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400 text-sm"
                        >
                            check_circle
                        </span>
                        RAG Pipelines for Knowledge Retrieval
                    </li>
                    <li
                        class="flex items-center gap-3 text-text-description dark:text-text-description-dark"
                    >
                        <span
                            class="material-symbols-outlined text-cyan-700 dark:text-cyan-400 text-sm"
                        >
                            check_circle
                        </span>
                        Workflow Automation (n8n, Make, Python)
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
